'''House Egen''' is a noble house from the [[Vale of Arryn]], sworn to [[House Arryn]], the [[Lord of the Eyrie|Lords of the Eyrie]] and [[Lord Paramount of the Vale|Lords Paramount of the Vale]]. They blazon their arms with a yellow sun, white crescent moon, and silver star on blue chief above white. Their motto is &quot;By Day or Night.&quot;
